spdlog is a very fast C++ logging library.

Features include:

- Feature rich formatting, using fmt
- Custom formatting
- Multi or single threaded loggers
- Various log targets:
  - Rotating log files
  - Daily log files
  - Console logging (colors supported)
  - syslog
- Log filtering - log levels can be modified at both run and compile times
- Support for loading log levels from argv or environment
- Backtrace support - store debug messages in a ring buffer for later display
